 (b) constructing and commissioning of the Huayu Plant to process the ore extracted from the Beikeng Mine. In FY2020, the Company had:

 (1)  completed the tunneling and upgrading of the necessary production, access and ventilation tunnels at the Beikeng Mine, including the construction of pullouts and replacement of aging arch supports;

 (2) installed electrical lighting and ventilation systems along the tunnels;

 (3) constructed a stock-pile area for ore extracted from the Beikeng Mine, and a system of access roads within and connecting to the Beikeng Mine;

 (4)  constructed, and obtained from the Public Security Bureau the license to operate, a secured magazine to store explosives used at the Beikeng Mine; and

 (5) kept all extraction, production safety and environmental protection licenses and approvals in good standing.
